{"word":"G3853 - παραγγέλλω - parangéllō - par-ang-gel'-lo - Charge","slug":"G3853","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">παραγγέλλω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>parangéllō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>par-ang-gel'-lo"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Charge"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C0;&#x03B1;&#x03C1;&#x03B1;&#x03B3;&#x03B3;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03BB;&#x03BB;&#x03C9; - paraggello&#x0304;</b> - <i>par-ang-gel'-lo</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G3844\">G3844</a> and the base of <a href=\"#/G32\">G32</a>; to <i>transmit a message</i>, that is, (by implication) to <i>enjoin:</i> - (give in) charge, (give) command (-ment), declare."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G3852\">G3852</a>"}]}